publicwhip.spmotion: *S1M-917 Roseanna Cunningham: Glasgow Rape Crisis Centre—That the Parliament commends and supports the Glasgow Rape Crisis Centre in its decision to seek a Judicial Review of the Home Secretary’s ruling allowing Michael Tyson to enter the UK.
